        <updateDate>2015-10-09T17:10:32Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to make permanent a recognition period of 5 years (currently, 10 years) of the built-in gains of an S corporation beginning on the date that such corporation qualifies as an S corporation. </p>]]></text>
